name: 6 Kings - King Riley
description:
Valiant and brave.
Pure crimson fire flows through his veins.
Tenacious, spirited and virile. There is no challenge or confrontation that he will not face.
He has no need for a wife yet the Queen's are all in line awaiting his hand.
His strong emotion and quick whit keep him ahead of his opposition. 
He feels sensitivity of his mother and fierce weapon handling from his father and brothers. There is no match. He is well aware yet he yearns for battle so there may no one who ever questions his readiness or ability.
